      <description>&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;ve been using the settings below from version 8 through 11.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;1-in-keyboard-settings-swap-the-shortcuts-for-select-the-previous-input-source-and-select-next-source-in-input-menu&#34;&gt;1. In keyboard settings, swap the shortcuts for &amp;ldquo;Select the previous input source&amp;rdquo; and &amp;ldquo;Select next source in Input menu&amp;rdquo;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;2015020501.png&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;https://kimpaper.github.io/images/2015020501.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;2-in-parallels-preferences-add-the-shortcut-mapping-below-commandspace---altgr&#34;&gt;2. In Parallels preferences, add the shortcut mapping below (Command+Space -&amp;gt; AltGr)&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;2015020502.png&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;https://kimpaper.github.io/images/2015020502.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Done. This worked for me.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
